June 30, 1975*

Vacated and Remanded on Appeal

No. 74-726. No. 74-5743. Sheldon, Hospital Superintendent v. Reynolds; and Reynolds v. Sheldon, Hospital Superintendent.

Mk. Justice Douglas took no part in the consideration or decision of cases in which orders hereinafter reported were announced on this date,

Appeals from D. C. N. D. Tex. Motions of Perry Wayne Reynolds for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted, judgment vacated, and cases remanded for further consideration in light of O’Connor v. Donaldson, ante, p. 563. Reported below: 381 F. Supp. 1374.
